Program: The Why Factor
Title: Tattoos
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01c0qnz
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 22 Jul 2013
In this programme, Mike Williams asks why people have tattoos. Where do they come from and what do they say about us? From the Maori of New Zealand to the Mexican Mafia, Mike explores the universal motivation behind why people decorate their bodies with ink. (Image: David Beckham's tattooed bare back. Credit: AFP/Getty Images) Show less